==位置及設計==
[[File:10.7.09BoulevardEast&60thSTByLuigiNovi1.jpg|thumb]]

經過多年在[[紐約都會區|紐約都會區]]尋找合適的地點後，這條賽道才被決定坐落於{{link-en|北河 (哈德遜河)|North River (Hudson River)|哈德遜河}}和{{link-en|哈德遜峭壁|Hudson Palisades}}旁，能夠一覽天際景觀和海拔變化，另外這裡也有方便的大眾運輸工具。<ref name="WSJ"/>

這是一條順時針方向的賽道，由德國賽道設計師[[赫爾曼·提爾克|赫爾曼·提爾克]]所設計。賽道的起跑線計畫毗鄰於{{link-en|紐約水上公路|NY Waterway}}的渡輪碼頭旁，而維修站和車庫則位於渡輪碼頭與帝國碼頭大道之間。賽道的第一段沿著整條{{link-en|哈得遜河海濱走廊|Hudson River Waterfront Walkway}}，旨在使賽車能夠跑過整個帝國港，之後在沿著{{link-en|潘興路 (威霍肯)|Pershing Road (Weehawken)|潘興路}}爬上哈德遜峭壁。接著來到{{link-en|東方大道|Boulevard East}}，一直到北端的唐納利紀念公園（Donnelly Memorial Park）後右轉下坡至山邊大道（Hillside Avenue），一直到盡頭後便是一個鄰近西紐約汙水處理廠的[[髮夾彎|髮夾彎]]。賽道最後一路沿著帝國碼頭大道向南回到帝國碼頭。<ref name="WSJ"/><ref>{{en}}{{Citation|last=Torres|first=Agustin C.|title=Formula One racing is a done deal for Hudson County's 'Monte Carlo'|newspaper=The Jersey Journal|date=25 October 2011|url=http://www.nj.com/hudson/voices/index.ssf/2011/10/formula_one_racing_is_a_done_d.html|accessdate=2011-10-29|archive-date=2018-09-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180918080053/https://www.nj.com/hudson/voices/index.ssf/2011/10/formula_one_racing_is_a_done_d.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>從帝國港至哈德遜峭壁的海拔高度變化將近{{convert|150|ft|m|abbr=off|sp=us}}，<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.statesman.com/sports/formula1/new-jersey-will-host-second-f1-event-in-1934006.html|title=New Jersey will host second F1 event in U.S.|last=Maher|first=John|date=25 October 2011|work=Austin American-Statesman|accessdate=2011-10-26|location=Austin, TX|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111028211728/http://www.statesman.com/sports/formula1/new-jersey-will-host-second-f1-event-in-1934006.html|archivedate=2011年10月28日}}</ref>使這條賽道成為賽曆中海拔高度變化最大的賽道之一。<ref name="F1B">{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.formula1blog.com/2011/04/14/vox-certatus-texas-is-flat-so-there-will-be-no-elevation-changes/|title=Vox Certatus: 'Texas is flat so there will be no elevation changes'|last=Greene|first=Tony|date=14 April 2011|publisher=Formula1Blog|accessdate=2011-10-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120402152209/http://www.formula1blog.com/2011/04/14/vox-certatus-texas-is-flat-so-there-will-be-no-elevation-changes/|archive-date=2012-04-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

儘管賽道會經過住宅區，但當地的居民並不會被驅趕；相關單位也打算造訪七個受影響的住宅區。另外主辦單位更計畫不接受任何政府補助金來舉辦這場賽事。<ref name="WSJ"/><ref>{{en}}{{Citation|last=Pope|first=Gennarose|title=Three-day race hits local streets in 2013|newspaper=Hudson Reporter|date=30 October 2011|url=http://www.hudsonreporter.com/view/full_story/16214733/article-Three-day-race-hits-local-streets-in-2013-Formula-One-cars-in-WNY--Weehawken-could-peak-at-200-MPH-?|accessdate=2011-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131108080133/http://www.hudsonreporter.com/view/full_story/16214733/article-Three-day-race-hits-local-streets-in-2013-Formula-One-cars-in-WNY--Weehawken-could-peak-at-200-MPH-|archive-date=2013-11-08|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

