先前計畫位於紐約河濱走廊渡輪碼頭，用來作為車隊司令部與裝備區的車庫建設在2012年7月動工，<ref>{{en}}{{cite web   | title = Weehawken Twp. and Roseland Property Company Break Ground on Ferry Parking Garage at Port Imperial   | author = Cahn Roundup   | date = July 7, 2011   | url = http://cahnroundup.com/2011/07/07/weehawken-twp-and-roseland-property-company-break-ground-on-ferry-parking-garage-at-port-imperial/   | accessdate = 2013-04-25   | archive-date = 2013-12-03   | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131203012415/http://cahnroundup.com/2011/07/07/weehawken-twp-and-roseland-property-company-break-ground-on-ferry-parking-garage-at-port-imperial/   | dead-url = no   }}</ref><ref name=prepares>{{en}}{{cite news   | last = Jones   | first = Satcy   | title = New Jersey's Gold Coast prepares for roaring engines of Formula One racers with eye on 2013 start   | newspaper = The Star-Ledger   | date = July 8, 2012   | url = http://www.nj.com/business/index.ssf/2012/07/new_jerseys_gold_coast_prepare.html   | accessdate = 2013-03-20   | quote =    | archive-date = 2018-09-18   | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180918080057/https://www.nj.com/business/index.ssf/2012/07/new_jerseys_gold_coast_prepare.html   | dead-url = no   }}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite news   | last = Pope   | first = Jennifer   | title = Building boom on the waterfront   | newspaper = Hudson Reporter   | date = 1969-12-31   | url = http://hudsonreporter.com/pages/full_stories_home/push?article-Building+boom+on+the+waterfront-Officials+break+ground+for+million-dollar+residences-%20&id=19849346&instance=weehawken_story_left_column   | accessdate = 2013-03-22   | quote = ... an 800-space parking garage and headquarters for the 2013 Port Imperial Grand Prix Formula One race is heading toward completion as well.   | archive-date = 2018-09-18   | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180918080105/http://hudsonreporter.com/pages/full_stories_home/push?article-Building+boom+on+the+waterfront-Officials+break+ground+for+million-dollar+residences-%20&id=19849346&instance=weehawken_story_left_column   | dead-url = no   }}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite news   | last = Strunsky   | first = Steve   | title = N.J. Formula 1 race, more bumps in the road   | newspaper = The Star-Ledger   | date = May 8, 2013   | url = http://www.nj.com/news/index.ssf/2013/05/for_nj_formula_1_race_more_bum.html#incart_river   | accessdate = 2013-05-08   | quote =    | archive-date = 2013-06-06   | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130606183514/http://www.nj.com/news/index.ssf/2013/05/for_nj_formula_1_race_more_bum.html#incart_river   | dead-url = no   }}</ref>共有24個維修車庫。<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|title=N.J. Formula One Race Is 'Definitely On'|url=http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424127887324299104578531323487479656.html|first=A.J.|last=Baine|work=[[The_Wall_Street_Journal|The Wall Street Journal]]|publisher=Lex Fenwick|date=7 June 2013|accessdate=8 June 2013|archive-date=2013-06-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130608130712/http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424127887324299104578531323487479656.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>並構想將建築物一樓作為零售空間，會隨著每年舉行的比賽而改變。<ref name=prepares/>最終在2013年夏季完工。而兩間飯店也在2013年11月動工，建於帝國港停車場上方。<ref>{{en}}{{cite news   | last = Sibayan   | first = Rose   | title = Weehawken breaks ground for two hotels to rise above Port Imperial parking garage   | newspaper = The Jersey Journal   | date = November 14, 2013   | url = http://www.nj.com/jjournal-news/index.ssf/2013/11/weehawken_breaks_ground_for_tw.html   | accessdate = 2013-11-16   | quote =    | archive-date = 2016-10-29   | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161029173727/http://www.nj.com/jjournal-news/index.ssf/2013/11/weehawken_breaks_ground_for_tw.html   | dead-url = no   }}</ref>

2013年6月，連接碼頭與輕軌車站間期待已久的天橋正式啟用，這被視為是大眾進入這條賽道最重要的一個地點。<ref>{{en}}{{cite news   | last = Wenik   | first = Ian   | title = Open at last - After long wait, pedestrian bridge connects light rail and ferry   | newspaper = Hudson Reporter   | date = June 9, 2013   | url = http://www.hudsonreporter.com/view/full_story/22842871/article-Open-at-last-After-long-wait--pedestrian-bridge-connects-light-rail-and-ferry-?instance=more_page   | accessdate = 2013-07-11   | quote =    | archive-date = 2017-01-18   | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170118135445/http://www.hudsonreporter.com/view/full_story/22842871/article-Open-at-last-After-long-wait--pedestrian-bridge-connects-light-rail-and-ferry-?instance=more_page   | dead-url = no   }}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite news   | last = Cichowksi   | first = John   | title = Road Warrior: $9.7M footbridge needs more feet   | newspaper = The Record   | date = June 11, 2013   | url = http://www.northjersey.com/columnists/cichowski/Road_Warrior_97M_footbridge_needs_more_feet.html?c=y&page=1   | accessdate = 2013-07-11   | quote =    | archive-date = 2013-12-03   | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131203040548/http://www.northjersey.com/columnists/cichowski/Road_Warrior_97M_footbridge_needs_more_feet.html?c=y&page=1   | dead-url = no   }}</ref>

在2013年8至11月間，完成了道路的重鋪和其他工程。<ref>{{en}}{{cite press release| title = FORMULA 1: Bus Route Nos. 23, 128, 165, 166 and 168: Boulevard East Detours due to Construction Work for Formula 1 - Beginning Mid-August 2013| publisher = New Jersey Transit| date = August 13, 2013| url = http://m.njtransit.com/mo/mo_servlet.srv?hdnPageAction=ServiceAdjustmentTo&AdjustmentId=10255&From=Bus| accessdate = 2013-08-31| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131225222448/http://m.njtransit.com/mo/mo_servlet.srv?hdnPageAction=ServiceAdjustmentTo&AdjustmentId=10255&From=Bus| archive-date = 2013-12-25| dead-url = yes}}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite news|title=New Jersey F1 Race Promoter Hindery Jr. Says 'We Are Back Under Construction'|url=http://www.sportsbusinessdaily.com/Global/Issues/2013/03/08/Events-and-Attractions/New-Jersey-F1.aspx|first=HJ|last=Mai|work=SportsBusiness Journal|date=March 8, 2013|accessdate=March 8, 2013|archive-date=2013-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130310050840/http://www.sportsbusinessdaily.com/Global/Issues/2013/03/08/Events-and-Attractions/New-Jersey-F1.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>為了創建一個平滑的路面，而分批完成重鋪工程，也不會使瀝青在倒入路面時冷卻。另外像是消防栓與號誌燈等的潛在的障礙物，還有待商榷是否要移除。<ref name=prepares/>

